casebody.data:
Juliet YACKEL, petitioner,
v.
SOUTH DAKOTA, et al. No. 18-553 (18A449). Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 29, 2018.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice GORSUCH and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of South Dakota denied.
